---
title: Sticky Glazed Chicken Breasts Sammies with Roasted Potato Rounds and Sesame Aioli
description: The ubiquitous flavours of Chinese take-out is embodied in this chicken sandwich! Juicy chicken thighs are slathered with a sweet and tangy sauce, then get a sesame aioli for another layer of complexity. There's also extra aioli for those potato coins!
